{
  "title": "Savory Turkish Paneer Tagine",
  "description": "A savory and comforting Turkish dish featuring paneer, this tagine is perfect for a cold winter night, with the flavors of the Mediterranean and a touch of flambe",
  "cuisine": "Turkish",
